### 机票预订系统 API 测试

### 获取所有活跃机场
GET http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/airports
Accept: application/json

###

### 搜索航班 - 北京到上海
GET http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/flights/search?departureAirport=PEK&arrivalAirport=SHA&departureDate=2024-12-15
Accept: application/json

###

### 搜索航班 - 上海到广州  
GET http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/flights/search?departureAirport=SHA&arrivalAirport=CAN&departureDate=2024-12-15
Accept: application/json

###

### 创建机票预订
POST http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flightId": "{{flightId}}",
  "passengerFirstName": "张",
  "passengerLastName": "三",
  "passengerEmail": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "passportNumber": "E12345678",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-15",
  "nationality": "中国",
  "seatsCount": 1,
  "cabinClass": 0
}

###

### 根据预订参考号查询预订
GET http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/bookings/{{bookingReference}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 确认预订
POST http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/bookings/{{bookingReference}}/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 取消预订
POST http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/bookings/{{bookingReference}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 获取乘客的所有预订
GET http://localhost:5130/api/FlightBooking/passengers/{{passengerId}}/bookings
Accept: application/json

###
